vulnerability.name: USN-2707-1
vulnerability.description: Cody Crews discovered a way to violate the same-origin policy to inject script in to a non-privileged part of the PDF viewer. If a user were tricked in to opening a specially crafted website, an attacker could exploit this to read sensitive information from local files. (CVE-2015-4495)

statements.status_notes: Firefox could be made to expose sensitive information from local files.
